imdb.plot outline: Five college geeks, Peter, Tien, Garret, Wesley and Leo try to navigate life as they know it. What might that be? Living in an cramped house that they can barely afford, trying to invent a groundbreaking artificial intelligence that will change society as we know it, and well, possibly selling drugs with their chemistry teacher. All while playing video games. With tuition rates rising, and Peter and Tien's chances of ever getting a girlfriend dwindling, they need help. Enter Casey and Mia. Casey? The cute new girl at the comic book shop. And Mia? A hot, but b**chy art student new to campus, with no place to stay. Will Peter and Tien ever stop embarrassing themselves enough to ask Casey on a date? Will Wesley's bright idea to get a girl in the house mean inviting Mia to live with them? Find out on GEEK IT.
